                  <xref href="callouts-preferences-page.dita#callouts-preferences-page"
                    ><uicontrol>Callouts</uicontrol> preferences page</xref>, the callouts are
                displayed in <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode for comments, tracked insertions, or
                tracked deletions.</p>
              <p id="p_ayy_bgk_54b">
                <dl id="dl_byy_bgk_54b">
