          <dlentry id="dlentry_yyy_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Insert</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
            <dd>
              <p id="p_zyy_bgk_54b">This submenu includes insert actions that are specific to each <xref
                  keyref="glossentry_framework"><term>framework</term></xref>, along with the
                following general action:</p>
              <p id="p_azy_bgk_54b">
                <dl id="dl_bzy_bgk_54b">
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_czy_bgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Insert Entity</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Allows you to insert a predefined entity or character entity. Surrogate
                      character entities (range #x10000 to #x10FFFF) are also accepted. Character
                      entities can be entered in one of the following forms: <ul id="ul_t3w_twm_ps">
                        <li id="li_dzy_bgk_54b">#<i>&lt;decimal value&gt;</i> - e. g. #65</li>
                        <li id="li_ezy_bgk_54b">&amp;#<i>&lt;decimal value&gt;</i>; - e. g. &amp;#65</li>
                        <li id="li_fzy_bgk_54b">#x<i>&lt;hexadecimal value&gt;</i> - e. g. #x41</li>
                        <li id="li_gzy_bgk_54b">&amp;#x<i>&lt;hexadecimal value&gt;</i>; - e. g. &amp;#x41</li>
                      </ul></dd>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
              </p>
            </dd>
