            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/PasteSpecialDITA16.png" id="image_us5_53h_ps"/>Paste
                special</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
            <dd>
              <p id="p_lzy_bgk_54b">This submenu includes special paste actions that are specific to each <xref
