                following general paste actions:</p>
              <p id="p_mzy_bgk_54b">
                <dl id="dl_nzy_bgk_54b">
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_ozy_bgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Paste As XML</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Pastes clipboard content that is considered to be XML, preserving its XML
                      structure.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_pzy_bgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Paste As Text</uicontrol> (<uicontrol
                        conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/ctrl_shift_v"/>)</dt>
                    <dd>Pastes clipboard content, ignoring any structure or styling markup.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
              </p>
            </dd>
